data.description: Here is a great home in the Town of Stuart. The house features three bedrooms and 2.5 baths. One level living and a location that puts you close to everything you need. As you enter though the front door you arrive at the large living room and just around the corner is the eat-in kitchen which has been updated. Down the hall is a large full bath, extra bedroom and a large full bath. The primary bedroom as an ensuite bath and a door leading to a small deck. The third bedroom has been used as a dining room but could easily be converted back into the third bedroom. There is a full basement with lots of storage and a half bath along with the laundry area. In the rear of the home there is a outbuilding for additional space or a workshop.
